title: Julia Haart is Brazen
description:
Oy vey Julia Haart has been through it. This week Claire and Ashley are combing through her torah-length memoir to understand her fundamentalist upbringing and how she busted outta there and became a She-EO and the star of a Netflix reality show only a few years later.
